{
  "stem": "17515.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 104.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 152,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I was living in the-- in the-- in that school.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 152,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And [INAUDIBLE], the wife of the president.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 153,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Many people was organized different way, some-- some-- a friend of mine been scared to-- about-- was thinking about joining the underground army.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 154,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 155,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had the opportunity, but I was too young, too naive.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 155,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was not even thinking about-- obviously is he going, I say nothing happen to me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 156,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Maybe, maybe a couple of months.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 156,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then I-- completely-- it was like deserted.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 157,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't show up anymore in the school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 157,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I-- I still be working as messenger for the-- for the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 157,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then I been living-- scary, scary.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 158,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I live in a-- a place, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 159,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, with that-- with that group.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 159,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But many people been already arrested by German.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 159,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was kind-- kind of scary place to live, even, at the time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 160,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My family used to live in Maciejowice, [? limited, ?] different town.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 160,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were safe there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 160,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But people who live Warsaw, it was very danger to live day by day.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 161,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When the-- when the-- the city was bombed, very much, now this is.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 161,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- the brought convoy, bread, giving bread to the people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 161,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they're standing by the-- by the water, watching everybody take the water, for the cooking, for the drinks.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 161,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was organized not so bad.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 162,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 163,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 164,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 165,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I've been working at-- yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 166,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I guess I can manage.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 167,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We've been very-- I lost track, that many people had been arrested before me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 167,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And many people then I hear actings, who tried to kill German, [INAUDIBLE] too, because it was scary to live in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 168,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 169,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I heard they've been-- been killed in the street.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 170,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was like a police, a martial law.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
